_sText:
Hello again, this is my second map submission.  I wanted to create something fun a unique for my gun game server.  Hope you guys enjoy.

You can play the map on my server here 72.36.145.10:27016.  You can find me under the name of [Aura]Ill knife ya!

Story: Terrorists have taken over a major corporate building and are demanding ransom.  They have already murdered many helpless employees.  The elite Counter-Terrorists unit has been called out and they have stormed the building.  The terrorists decide to dig in and make their stand in the inner courtyard of the building.  Who will be the victor?

Special thanks to [Aura] clan for testing and Interlopers forums for the help.
